text: Keenan Vieira (born 1 November 1997) is a South African cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Eastern Province in the 2018–19 CSA 3-Day Provincial Cup on 21 March 2019. He made his List A debut for Eastern Province in the 2018–19 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 24 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Eastern Province cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
